class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/48103/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/31186/" data-original="http://pic.youku778.com/upload/vod/2019-01-17/154766368914.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">9.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">10</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/31186/">鬼入侵</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E7%B1%B3%E5%A5%91%E5%B0%94%C2%B7%E5%93%88%E6%80%9D%E6%9B%BC------------/" target="_blank">米契尔·哈思曼</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%8D%A1%E6%8B%89%C2%B7%E5%8F%A4%E5%A5%87%E8%AF%BA------------/" target="_blank">卡拉·古奇诺</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E4%BA%A8%E5%88%A9%C2%B7%E6%89%98%E9%A9%AC%E6%96%AF------------/" target="_blank">亨利·托马斯</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E4%BC%8A%E8%8E%89%E8%8E%8E%E7%99%BD%C2%B7%E9%87%8C%E7%91%9F------------/" target="_blank">伊莉莎白·里瑟</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E8%BF%88%E5%85%8B%C2%B7%E5%BC%97%E6%8B%89%E7%BA%B3%E6%A0%B9--------/" target="_blank">迈克·弗拉纳根</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/16/" target="_blank">欧美剧</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD-----------/" target="_blank">美国</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2018/" target="_blank">2018</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>《鬼入侵》是雪莉·杰克逊同名经典小说的现代改编版，讲述了在美国最有名的鬼屋中长大的五个兄弟姐妹的故事成年后，他们因为最小的妹妹的自杀而重新聚到一起，迫使他们最终面对与自身过往有关的鬼魂，一些潜伏在他们的心中，还有一些潜伏在这幢著名的山之屋（Hill House）的阴暗处。</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/31186/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/15086/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2018-12-24/201812241545656640.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">8.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/15086/">活死人入侵</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E6%B1%9F%E5%85%B0%E8%90%B1------------/" target="_blank">江兰萱</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%88%98%E5%A4%A9%E5%AE%9D------------/" target="_blank">刘天宝</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E4%BD%95%E6%9F%94%E7%86%B9------------/" target="_blank">何柔熹</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%99%88%E5%BA%B7------------/" target="_blank">陈康</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E7%8E%8B%E5%AE%8F%E5%88%9A------------/" target="_blank">王宏刚</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E9%82%93%E5%AE%89%E4%B8%9C--------/" target="_blank">邓安东</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-------------/" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/6/" target="_blank">动作片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2017/" target="_blank">2017</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>讲述在地球被丧尸病毒侵袭后，蒋大卫一直与奶奶生活在地下室，在灾难到来时却因此而幸免于难他救下被丧尸群袭击的三个学生和一对在工地上干苦力的夫妇，不料厄运就此降临地下室。末日世界，人心比丧尸更可怕，因为人为了生存，什么都干得出来。在战胜坏人之后，蒋大卫与剩余的幸存者逃出了地下室……</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/15086/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/40055/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2018-11-22/201811221542884464.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">7.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/40055/">古墓入侵者</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-GinaVitori------------/" target="_blank">GinaVitori</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-SamanthaBowling------------/" target="_blank">SamanthaBowling</a>&nbsp